WEBVTT

00:05:59.400 --> 00:06:01.816
because I didn't pass the medical.

00:06:01.840 --> 00:06:05.136
The official reason
that I was denied my job

00:06:05.160 --> 00:06:11.976
was paralysis of poliomyelitis
sequelae of -- I'm sorry.

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:16.536
Paralysis of both lower limbs,
sequelae of poliomyelitis.

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:19.176
Honestly, I didn't know
what the word "sequelae" meant,

00:06:19.200 --> 00:06:22.496
so I went to the dictionary,
and it meant "because of."

00:06:22.520 --> 00:06:25.720
So I'd been denied my license
because I couldn't walk.

00:06:26.600 --> 00:06:29.176
So what was I going to do?

00:06:29.200 --> 00:06:32.256
This is a really important
time in my life,